You scream "don't bite me!" and the bee says "I'm not a bee, I'm your guardian angel. I'm here to tell you that you're not allergic, it was a lie. 

It is the middle of the night and no one is protecting you. You do not know how this bee got in your room. You hope your mom heard your scream but you want to know about this lie. You know that if you call your mother, she'll be mad at the bee. You demand the bee tell you why your mother would lie. The bee just says "To protect you." You don't understand and the bee explains "You're a princess." You are destined for a life of royalty when you are an adult. You will be a queen.
